sj = StringJoiner(prefix='[', suffix=']')
sj.add('e1').add('e2').add(3)
sj[3] = 'e4'
self.assertEqual('[e1,e2,3,e4]', str(sj))
expected__repr__ = (
    '{"separator": ",", "prefix": "[", "suffix": "]", "nelem": 4, "str_length": 12, "elements": ["e1", "e2", "3", "e4"]}'
    )
self.assertEqual(expected__repr__, sj.__repr__())
